The fair values of share-based awards vested in 2022, 2021 and 2020 were $ 93.0 million, $ 73.8 million and $ 62.7 million. Cash dividends paid for the vested awards were $ 9.6 million, $ 8.7 million and $ 9.4 million for 2022, 2021 and 2020. 

&#160; 

In relation to our equity compensation plans, we recognized $ 6.7 million in windfall tax benefits for the year ended December 31, 2022 , $ 1.6 million and $ 2.0 million of tax deficiencies for the years ended December 31, 2021 and 2020, respectively. 

